{"tid":1104073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柯士甸道西9號Grand Austin 失業澳洲籍籍男子燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-04-13T00:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T02:10:03.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3b09478efcbdb085358c832e04c9e2f911dc1946","tid":1104073,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴柯士甸道西9號Grand Austin一單位，凌晨近4時，46歲澳洲籍男子John，在廚房內燒炭昏迷，其姓李34歲女友發現報警。救護員接報到場，證實男事主已死亡。警方在現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據知John最近失業，疑因此事輕生。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=8481bd92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190413/59483264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190413%2F59483264&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=c79d4f95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190413%2F59483264&h=ddb07726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190413/59483264</a>"},{"pid":"6b80472cdc861a6556886fdc475addf9736be0d6","tid":1104073,"uid":4258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"應該係租租？"},{"pid":"67ecba35ef1d2f11098c45dd32159c1d0356130d","tid":1104073,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"業主：mola mola<br />\n租租或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ag